  "texts": [
    "We provide example generated answers and retrieved documents in Table A3 and Table A4 for Databricks and Faire, respectively.",
    "In Table A3, the weaker retrievers fail to find the relevant document given the user's query.",
    "As a result, the generative models also fail to provide the correct answer.",
    "This shows the benefit of training and using more accurate retrievers.",
    "In Table A4, despite all methods retrieved the correct document, the weaker generative models failed to incorporate all relevant information in its response."
